Text:
sweet, I jsut found out ther's a season 2 and 3 AND a movie

thx

Episodes are fairly low quality, and are direct from TV rips, so yes, they are censored.

Better than nothing, I guess. Thanks.
Why do you have to find uncensored? Is it really a big deal? Are you unable to watch the show because there is a beep instead of a "shit"?

Just so people don't save it for last and then get disappointed like I did: The movie is nothing but clips from Season 3 sewn together. They changed a handful of scenes, but if you've seen season 3, then you've seen the movie.

Seasons 1 & 2 are ripped straight from The SciFi Channel. The video quality of season 1 is grainy with full screen resolution (512*384). The video quality of season 2 is still full screen (512*384) but there is no graininess. Season 3 is a wide screen (672*368) DVDRip. The video quality is very good.
Thank you spider_x. I just wanted to point out that the pilot episode is not included, but its not a big deal. Thank you again for the upload.
maaannn... I fucking love you for this, but in a non prison cellmate way :D
